# Files excluded from `git archive` output (GitHub Release source archives,
# and scripts/build_release_archive.sh, both use this). These are AI-agent
# operating instructions and internal AI-TDD process artifacts, not part of
# the router itself. Keep this the single source of truth for what a release
# archive excludes; do not duplicate this list elsewhere.
#
# docs/architecture/ and docs/specs/ are NOT excluded: they document the
# router's own design, not AI operating process, and are useful to a
# downstream consumer of the released code.
AGENTS.md export-ignore
CLAUDE.md export-ignore
.github/copilot-instructions.md export-ignore
docs/at-tdd/ export-ignore
docs/collaboration/ export-ignore
docs/templates/ export-ignore
docs/issues/ export-ignore
docs/work-plans/ export-ignore
docs/evaluation/ export-ignore
